videos.description: Utah State's Suli Tamaivena picks up the botched snap from Wisconsin and returns it into the red zone.
videos.headline: Aggies take advantage of Badgers' bobbled snap

videos.description: Utah State RB LaJuan Hunt takes the handoff and runs it into the end zone for the 12-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Aggies' Hunt rushes into the end zone

videos.description: Aggies DB Jalen Davis is thrown out of the game for after helmet-to-helmet hit on Wisconsin WR Quintez Cephus.
videos.headline: Davis ejected for targeting

videos.description: Wisconsin running back Bradrick Shaw dives into the end zone for a 3-yard touchdown for the first Badgers touchdown of the season.
videos.headline: Shaw leaps into the end zone to put Wisconsin on board

videos.description: T.J. Edwards intercepts the pass from Kent Myers to set up Wisconsin in the red zone late in the first half.
videos.headline: Badgers get the INT off the deflection

videos.description: Wisconsin head coach Paul Chryst discusses first half mistakes and what his team needs to do in the second.
videos.headline: Wisconsin head coach Paul Chryst talks about uncharacteristic half

videos.description: Jonathan Taylor takes the first snap of the second half into Utah State territory with a run of 41-yards.
videos.headline: Wisconsin's Taylor opens 2nd half with 41-yard run

videos.description: Alex Hornibrook finds Troy Fumagalli wide open downfield who takes the pass into the end zone for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Hornibrook connects with Fumagalli for the Badger TD

videos.description: D'Cota Dixon picks off the pass downfield from Kent Myers for the second interception of the day for Wisconsin.
videos.headline: Dixon with the 2nd Badgers' INT of game

videos.description: Zander Neuville's first career catch is a touchdown that puts Wisconsin up two scores.
videos.headline: Neuville takes in another Wisconsin TD

videos.description: Jonathan Taylor jukes out of the way of his own offensive line and runs for the pylon for his first career touchdown.
videos.headline: Taylor dodges own offensive line for the TD

videos.description: Quintez Cephus makes a nice grab on the back-shoulder pass for his first career touchdown reception.
videos.headline: Cephus with the back-shoulder TD catch

videos.description: Wisconsin FB Austin Ramesh takes the handoff on the sweep and runs nearly untouched into the end zone.
videos.headline: Ramesh runs in another Badgers TD

videos.description: Redshirt freshman Garrett Groshek dives into the end zone for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Grosheck dives into the end zone for the TD

videos.description: Wisconsin TE talks about how his team got back into the game and his new number in honor of his injured teammate.
videos.headline: Troy Fumagalli discusses his new number in honor of his teammate

videos.description: Adam Amin and Dusty Dvoracek discuss Wisconsin's 59 unanswered points after starting the game down 10-0 to Utah State.
videos.headline: Breaking down Wisconsin's 59-10 win over Utah State

videos.description: Down 10-0 in the first quarter, Wisconsin scores 59-unanswered points and Alex Hornibrook throws for three touchdowns and the Badgers rush for four scores in a 59-10 victory over Utah State.
videos.headline: Slow start doesn't stop Wisconsin from onslaught in opener
